import React from 'react'; import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Paper, Timeline, TimelineItem, TimelineSeparator, TimelineConnector, TimelineContent, TimelineDot, Card, CardContent, } from '@mui/material'; const milestones = [ { year: '2008', title: 'Establishment', description: 'Sri Eshwar College of Engineering was established' }, { year: '2012', title: 'NBA Accreditation', description: 'First NBA accreditation received' }, { year: '2015', title: 'Research Center', description: 'Recognized as Research Center by Anna University' }, { year: '2020', title: 'NAAC A+ Grade', description: 'Awarded NAAC A+ grade with 3.47 CGPA' }, { year: '2024', title: 'Top Rankings', description: '15th Position in Tamil Nadu, 7th Rank in Coimbatore' } ]; const values = [ { title: 'Vision', content: 'To be a Premier Technological Institution offering Contemporary Technical Education and Research focusing on Holistic Development of individuals for the benefit of society.' }, { title: 'Mission', content: [ 'To provide quality technical education through experiential learning.', 'To establish Centers of Excellence in emerging technologies.', 'To create an ecosystem for innovative research and entrepreneurship.', 'To develop competent and ethical professionals with social responsibility.', 'To foster industry-institution collaboration for mutual benefit.' ] } ]; const About = () => { return ( {/* Hero Section */} About SECE Empowering minds, shaping futures since 2008 {/* Overview Section */} Excellence in Education Sri Eshwar College of Engineering (SECE) is a premier institution offering quality technical education with a focus on holistic development. Located in the educational hub of Coimbatore, we have established ourselves as one of the top engineering colleges in Tamil Nadu. Our institution is approved by AICTE, New Delhi and affiliated to Anna University, Chennai. We have been accredited with 'A+' Grade by NAAC with CGPA of 3.47 out of 4.00 scale. With state-of-the-art infrastructure, experienced faculty, and strong industry connections, we prepare our students for successful careers in the ever-evolving technological landscape. {/* Vision & Mission */} Vision & Mission {values.map((value) => ( {value.title} {Array.isArray(value.content) ? (

) : ( {value.content} )} ))} {/* Milestones */} Our Journey {milestones.map((milestone, index) => ( {index !== milestones.length - 1 && } {milestone.year} {milestone.title} {milestone.description} ))} {/* Achievements Section */} Our Achievements 15th Position in Tamil Nadu A+ NAAC Grade 50+ Global Partners 100% Placement Record ); }; export default About;
